text: Yahya Abdul-Aziz Jemus Junkung Jammeh (; born 25 May 1965)Country Profiles: Sub-Saharan Africa: Gambia, U.K. Foreign & Commonwealth Office, 18 July 2011 . is a Gambian politician. He became the president of The Gambia in 1994. ==References== ==Other websites== * Jammeh to Hizbullah TV: We Support Iran's Nuclear Program; All Countries Are Entitled to Obtain Nuclear Weapons Until These Are Abolished Category:1965 births Category:Living people Category:African military people Category:Presidents of the Gambia Category:Colonels
